NUTCH-2281 Support non-default FileSystem

Instead of
  FileSystem fs = FileSystem.get(getConf());
use
  FileSystem fs = path.getFileSystem(getConf());
to avoid that FileSystem and Path match.

JEXL-123:
Refactored Introspector, ClassMap and MethodKey: simplified class, removed method, use lock and ConcurrentHashMap;
Removed parser classes from cobertura report;
Aligned pom with 2.1;

