Make namespaces in .i.js files contain `{}`

Previously, we were translating definitions of the form
     /** @const */ var goog = goog || {};
to
     /** @const */ var goog;
in .i.js files.  Now we will instead generate
     /** @const */ var goog = {};

This makes the generated files compatible with NTI.

